        "description": "Your body is an indestructible weapon, augmented with cutting-edge cyberware that blurs the line between man and machine. You're fast, brutal, and surgical in a fight, trained in tactics and hardened by your past life to mercilessly eliminate the opposition. But you don't kill without reason. Maintaining some honor, and a shred of humanity, means something to you, even if no one else in this line of work cares. You've got the skills to sneak by the opposition when you can, but if that doesn't work, you make sure you and your team get out alive.\n\nKeep your Firearms Skill Mastery talent and your Aluminum Bone Lacing cyberware in mind - whenever you attack with a firearm, or when you make an Armor test, you score a critical hit if both of your Crit Dice are a 5 or a 6 (not just if they're both 6's)."
